1823
01:32:32.766 --> 01:32:35.102
Via!

1824
01:32:36.770 --> 01:32:40.273
Dovete andarvene!

1825
01:32:44.277 --> 01:32:48.407
Dobbiamo evacuare l'area!

1826
01:32:56.915 --> 01:32:57.916
